{"id":1540,"category_slug":"toeic","category_name":"TOEIC Listening","position":308,"title":"Conversation 158","subtitle":"Movie Night Invitation","level":"B1","parts":13,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/toeic/conversation-158.1540/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-158-2024-09-14-18-24-02/0-conversation-158.mp3","transcript":"Hey, Emma.\nThe new Anthony Eyre movie just came out last weekend.\nAre you interested?\nHa! Thought you would never ask.\nBut my aunt's coming for a visit,\nand I'm supposed to pick her up at the airport around 6 pm.\nHowever, she loves watching movies,\nso why don't we invite her and watch the new movie together?\nYou've met her, right?\nOf course, she's so much fun.\nAnd I seem to remember she's a huge fan of Anthony Eyre.\nWell, drive safe.\nI'll meet you at the movie theater on Burrard and Cambie Street.","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T21:02:24","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Hey, Emma.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-158-2024-09-14-18-24-02/1.mp3","time_start":0.0,"time_end":0.92},{"position":2,"content":"The new Anthony Eyre movie just came out last weekend.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-158-2024-09-14-18-24-02/2.mp3","time_start":0.92,"time_end":4.05},{"position":3,"content":"Are you interested?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-158-2024-09-14-18-24-02/3.mp3","time_start":4.05,"time_end":5.27},{"position":4,"content":"Ha! Thought you would never ask.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-158-2024-09-14-18-24-02/4.mp3","time_start":5.27,"time_end":7.96},{"position":5,"content":"But my aunt's coming for a visit,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-158-2024-09-14-18-24-02/5.mp3","time_start":7.96,"time_end":9.9},{"position":6,"content":"and I'm supposed to pick her up at the airport around 6 pm.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-158-2024-09-14-18-24-02/6.mp3","time_start":9.9,"time_end":13.7},{"position":7,"content":"However, she loves watching movies,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-158-2024-09-14-18-24-02/7.mp3","time_start":13.88,"time_end":16.99},{"position":8,"content":"so why don't we invite her and watch the new movie together?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-158-2024-09-14-18-24-02/8.mp3","time_start":16.99,"time_end":20.62},{"position":9,"content":"You've met her, right?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-158-2024-09-14-18-24-02/9.mp3","time_start":20.62,"time_end":22.12},{"position":10,"content":"Of course, she's so much fun.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-158-2024-09-14-18-24-02/10.mp3","time_start":22.12,"time_end":24.54},{"position":11,"content":"And I seem to remember she's a huge fan of Anthony Eyre.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-158-2024-09-14-18-24-02/11.mp3","time_start":24.54,"time_end":28.02},{"position":12,"content":"Well, drive safe.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-158-2024-09-14-18-24-02/12.mp3","time_start":28.02,"time_end":29.48},{"position":13,"content":"I'll meet you at the movie theater on Burrard and Cambie Street.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-158-2024-09-14-18-24-02/13.mp3","time_start":29.48,"time_end":32.87}]}